import React from 'react'
import { SectionWrapper, Container, Box,GridWrapper, FlexWrapper, TextBase } from '@components/wrappers'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import AnimatedVideo from '@components/AnimatedVideo'
import TipTopApp from '@assets/videos/3d-phone-chrome.webm'

const JoinTipTopStyles = styled(SectionWrapper)`
    background-color: var(--lbg);
`

const JoinTipTop:React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <JoinTipTopStyles>
        <Container>
            <GridWrapper>
                <Box><AnimatedVideo srcChrome={TipTopApp} srcSafari='https://tiptop-media.s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/mp4/3d-phone-safari.mov' /></Box>
                <Box></Box>
            </GridWrapper>
        </Container>
    </JoinTipTopStyles>
  )
}

export default JoinTipTop
